query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.nome,
  p.createdAt,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clientes c WHERE c.projectId = p.id) as total_clientes,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM concorrentes co WHERE co.projectId = p.id) as total_concorrentes,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l WHERE l.projectId = p.id) as total_leads
FROM projects p
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
